# Scroll Receipt — environment variables

## Extension (apps/extension/.env)

```env
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key
```

Never commit real keys. Use Chrome extension build-time injection only for **anon** key.

## Supabase Edge Functions (secrets)

Set via Supabase Dashboard → Edge Functions → Secrets, or CLI:

```bash
supabase secrets set RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
supabase secrets set RESEND_FROM="Scroll Receipt <receipts@yourdomain.com>"
supabase secrets set SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_service_role_key
```

Auto-injected by Supabase: `SUPABASE_URL`, `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`.

## Cron

Schedule `daily-receipt` every 5 minutes via Supabase Dashboard → Integrations → Cron, or pg_cron.

Example curl (after deploy):

```bash
curl -X POST "$SUPABASE_URL/functions/v1/daily-receipt" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY"
```
